Package net.sf.jpam.jaas Description 

    This package contains the public JAAS API for using jpam.

    JAAS is included in JDK1.4 and higher as the javax.security.auth
    package. For versions of Java less than that, it is available as
    a separate download at http://java.sun.com/products/jaas/
